{"_id":"testimonial-seed-tenant-1","_type":"testimonial","quote":[{"_key":"en","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"en","value":"Maintenance requests get handled fast, and the team is always respectful and easy to reach."},{"_key":"es","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"es","value":"Las solicitudes de mantenimiento se atienden rápido, y el equipo siempre es respetuoso y fácil de contactar."}],"attribution":"D. Nguyen, Tenant","source":"tenant","featured":true,"order":1}
{"_id":"testimonial-seed-google-1","_type":"testimonial","quote":[{"_key":"en","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"en","value":"Found us the perfect rental in Spring Valley within a week. Professional, responsive, and genuinely helpful throughout."},{"_key":"es","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"es","value":"Nos encontraron el alquiler perfecto en Spring Valley en una semana. Profesionales, receptivos y realmente serviciales en todo momento."}],"attribution":"Google review","source":"google","featured":true,"order":2}
{"_id":"testimonial-seed-owner-2","_type":"testimonial","quote":[{"_key":"en","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"en","value":"They handled a tricky tenant transition smoothly and kept me informed every step of the way."},{"_key":"es","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"es","value":"Manejaron una transición de inquilinos complicada sin problemas y me mantuvieron informado en cada paso."}],"attribution":"The Whitfields, Property Owners","source":"owner","featured":false,"order":3}
{"_id":"testimonial-seed-tenant-2","_type":"testimonial","quote":[{"_key":"en","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"en","value":"Move-in was smooth and the leasing process was clear from start to finish."},{"_key":"es","_type":"internationalizedArrayTextValue","language":"es","value":"La mudanza fue sencilla y el proceso de arrendamiento fue claro de principio a fin."}],"attribution":"R. Castillo, Tenant","source":"tenant","featured":false,"order":4}
